---
// Process.astro — Growth Partner Alberta (updated with new data)
---

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-950 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-600 to-purple-600 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/3 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-600 to-pink-600 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tight">
        Our
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-400 to-fuchsia-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Growth Partner</span>
        process
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        We don’t sell deliverables — we operate growth systems. Below is how we take Alberta owner‑led businesses from
        <span class="text-slate-200">proof</span> → <span class="text-slate-200">foundation</span> → <span class="text-slate-200">growth</span> → <span class="text-slate-200">scale</span>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Process Steps (4 pillars) -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
      <!-- Step 1: 72h Sprint -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center"><span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl">1</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Free 72‑Hour Growth Sprint</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">Visible improvement in 3 days — no contracts. We fix one high‑impact area and deliver a 2‑minute Loom with before/after proof.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
              <li>• Website speed & conversion clarity <span class="text-slate-400">or</span> Google Business Profile visibility</li>
              <li>• Baseline metrics, daily updates, final proof video</li>
              <li>• Ideal fit validation for 30–90 day growth plan</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Setup Month -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center"><span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl">2</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Setup Month — Foundation & Ownership</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">One‑time setup: we build the technical base and hand you ownership. No retainer in month 1.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
              <li>• Website/Store, tracking (GA4, Tag Manager), dashboards</li>
              <li>• Google Business Profile creation/optimization & verification</li>
              <li>• Ads structure ready (Google, Bing, Meta) + CRO baseline</li>
              <li>• Repos, hosting, domain & DNS documented; you own assets</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: Growth Engine -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center"><span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl">3</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">90‑Day Growth Engine</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">Fixed retainer from month 2. We run your growth system and report results with clarity.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
              <li>• Weeks 1–3: Foundation hardening & speed/SEO structure</li>
              <li>• Weeks 4–6: Design refresh, copy, A/B & conversion paths</li>
              <li>• Weeks 7–10: Launch & optimize ads + GBP posting cadence</li>
              <li>• Weeks 11–13: Scale, report, and Blueprint handover</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4: Support & Scale -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center"><span class="text-white font-bold text-2xl">4</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ongoing Growth & Support</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">We operate, improve, and support. Monthly strategy calls, proactive fixes, and clear reporting.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
              <li>• Normal or Premium Support (SLA‑based response)</li>
              <li>• Monthly growth call + upsell roadmap when relevant</li>
              <li>• Churn prevention playbook: check‑ins every 3 weeks</li>
              <li>• System Blueprint updates & ownership hygiene</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mini "How we onboard" strip -->
    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-2">Onboarding</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Sales call → onboarding scheduled. Centralized form (Notion/Google), access invites, Drive folder, and kick‑off checklist.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-2">Access & Ownership</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">GBP Manager, GA4/Tag Manager, Ads MCC link, domain/DNS, repo & hosting. Client owns assets after setup.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-2">Communication</h4>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Daily short updates during sprint, weekly Loom in setup, monthly strategy calls in retainer.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline (90‑day view) -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">90‑Day Growth Timeline</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400">Clear milestones from proof to scale. Most projects start with the 72‑Hour Sprint.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline Line -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 h-full w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-violet-500 to-fuchsia-500 rounded-full"></div>

        <div class="space-y-16">
          <!-- Sprint -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12 text-right pr-8">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Day 0–3</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Free 72‑Hour Sprint (proof)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-violet-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950 z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Foundation -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-fuchsia-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950 z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-5/12 pl-8">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Weeks 1–3</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Foundation & Setup (ownership ready)</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Design/Optimization -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12 text-right pr-8">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Weeks 4–6</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Design refresh, SEO structure, CRO</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950 z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Growth Engine -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950 z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-5/12 pl-8">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Weeks 7–10</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Ads live, GBP posting, A/B testing</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Scale & Handover -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12 text-right pr-8">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Weeks 11–13</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Scale, reporting, Blueprint handover</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950 z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Ongoing -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-5/12"></div>
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-teal-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950 z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-5/12 pl-8">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Ongoing</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-400">Support tiers, monthly strategy, upsell roadmap</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/sprint" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 to-fuchsia-600 text-white font-semibold shadow-lg shadow-fuchsia-600/20 hover:opacity-95 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-fuchsia-400/60">Start the 72‑Hour Sprint</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl px-6 py-3 bg-slate-800 text-slate-200 font-semibold hover:bg-slate-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-500/60">Book an Onboarding Call</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
